      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIMBER JACK (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Moses Magic (18.73) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Capable of going well again. SCOTCH ALL ROUND (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (19.00) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Can do much better this time. ONE LAST SHOT (1) started long odds but took maiden two back then finished a 10 length fifth last start at this track over 318m (19.03). Nicely drawn here. Well placed here and can atone this time.",
